Moritz von Schwind January 1804 February 1871 was Austrian painter born Vienna Schwinds genius was lyricalhe drew inspiration from chivalry folklore and the songs the people Schwind died Pcking Bavaria and was buried the Alter Sdfriedhof Munich Moritz von Schwind received rudimentary training and spent happy and carefree youth Vienna Among his companions was the composer Schubert some whose songs illustrated 1828 the year Schuberts death moved Munich where befriended the painter Schnorr and enjoyed the guidance Cornelius then director the Academy 1834 was commissioned decorate King Ludwigs new palace with wall paintings illustrating the works the poet Tieck also found the same place congenial sport for his fancy Kinderfries was often busy working almanacs and illustrating Goethe and other writers through which gained considerable recognition and employment the revival art Germany Schwind held his own the sphere poetic fancy 1839 was entrusted with the new Karlsruhe academy itself embodiment fresco ideas thrown out Goethe decorated villa Leipzig with the story Cupid and Psyche and further justified his title poetpainter with designs from the Niebelungenlied and Tassos Gerusalemme for the walls the castle Hohenschwangau Bavaria From the year 1844 dates his residence Frankfurt during which created some his finest easel pictures most notably the Singers Contest the Wartburg 1846 well designs for the Goethe celebration There were also numerous book illustrations The conceptions for the most part are better than the execution 1847 Schwind returned Munich being appointed professor the academy Eight years later his fame was its height the completion the castle the Wartburg wall pictures illustrative the Singers Contest and the history Elizabeth Hungary The compositions received universal praise and grand musical festival their honour Schwind himself was one the violinists Munich also worked some churches particularly the altar and windows the Church Our Lady His exceptionally mature cycle Seven Ravens from Grimms fairy stories was produced 1857 the same year visited England report officially King Ludwig the Manchester art treasures diversified were his gifts that turned his hand church windows and joined his old friend Schnorr designs for the painted glass Glasgow Cathedral Towards the close his career with broken health and his powers the wane revisited Vienna During this time created the cycle from the legend Melusine and the designs commemorative chief musicians which decorate the foyer the Vienna State Opera Cornelius writes You have translated the joy music into pictorial art Player with Hermit Honey moon 1867 The prisoners dream Rbezahl Sabina Steinbach Abschied Morgengrauen Der Besuch Frau Maria Theresia Schwind Abenteuer des Malers Joseph Binder 